						<p>Pāṇḍya, Rājarāja Sundarapāṇḍya, 14th year, Āni = A.D. 1265.</p>						

						<p>Records that the trustees of Tiruvaraṅguḷam-uḍaiya-nāyaṉār temple agreed to supply oil to lamps on receiving a land endowment from the <hi rend="italic">nagarattār</hi> of Arumoḻidēva-puram.</p>						

